            "title": "美元兌一籃子貨幣走弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元兌一籃子貨幣繼續走弱，美元指數一度觸及99.209，較早時報99.235，跌幅近0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日圓兌美元上望142關口，一度升至142.26，較早時1美元報142.44日圓，跌近0.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新西蘭元兌美元升1%，澳元及歐元兌美元都升約0.5%。美元兌人民幣跌至約7.3水平，韓元兌美元亦由跌轉升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14853683-%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e5%85%8c%e4%b8%80%e7%b1%83%e5%ad%90%e8%b2%a8%e5%b9%a3%e8%b5%b0%e5%bc%b1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240410_source-licensed_USD_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 15:50:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "嘉亨灣中層全海景3房套 累減120萬元易手  原業主帳面獲利約420萬元離場",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港置業東區嘉亨灣分行表示，嘉亨灣本月錄首宗買賣成交，該行日前促成一宗該屋苑的買賣成交，新買家斥1,330萬元購入3房套，實用呎價約19,762元，屬市價成交。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述售出單位為嘉亨灣1座中層B室，實用面積約673平方呎，屬3房獨套間隔，向北享全海景。原業主以約1,450萬元放盤約1個半月後獲外區客洽詢，雙方經議價後，累減120萬元，以約1,330萬元成交，實用呎價約19,762元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">資料顯示，原業主於2010年1月以約910萬元購入上述單位，原業主帳而獲利約420萬元離場。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14853614-%e5%98%89%e4%ba%a8%e7%81%a3%e4%b8%ad%e5%b1%a4%e5%85%a8%e6%b5%b7%e6%99%af3%e6%88%bf%e5%a5%97-%e7%b4%af%e6%b8%9b120%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%98%93%e6%89%8b-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%b3%e9%9d%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 15:31:07",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股全日升 電商股向好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股全日收升，電商股午後造好，憧憬出口外貿轉戰內地市場，此外今早公布的出口數據勝預期。兩市合計成交12774.73億元(人民幣‧下同)。 </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日收報3262點，升24點或0.76%，今早以3251點開市，升13點或0.42%。最低見3244點，升6點或0.19%，為全日低位，升幅隨即擴大，最高見3272點，升34點或1.05%，為全日高位，全日成交5438.11億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日升49點或0.51%，報9884點，今日開市報9955點，更漲121點或1.23%，最高見9964點，升130點或1.32%，其後回落，下午見9862點，升幅收窄至28點或0.28%，為全日低位，全日成交7336.62億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數全日報3759點，升8點或0.23%，今日開升21點或0.57%，開報3772點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日升6點或0.34%，報1932點，今早開市報1954點，升27點或1.44%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國3月以美元計價出口按年升12.4%，貿易順差1026.4億美元，均超過預期。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美貿易戰持續，出口外貿企業要轉戰國內市場，有平台已推出助力計劃。電商股午後活躍，康力源(301287.SZ)升20%，報35.4元、久祺股份(300994.SZ)升19.98%，報13.57元、新華都(002264.SZ)升10.09%，報6.33元、南寧百貨(600712.SH)升10.08%，報7.1元、富嶺股份(001356.SZ)升10.03%，報17.34元、英派斯(002899.SZ)升10.02%，報21.09元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14853595-a%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87-%e9%9b%bb%e5%95%86%e8%82%a1%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 15:25:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
