            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南韓股市升近1%收市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首爾綜合指數收報2455點，升23點，升幅0.95%。</p>\n</div>",
